    "asOf": "2021-02-05",
    "date": "2021-04-13T13:25:54Z",
    "text": "Reinforcing Impaired Driving Education Act of 2021 or the RIDE Act of 2021\n\nThis bill requires the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration to establish a two-year pilot program to create and study the effects of a public marketing campaign to raise awareness on driving while under the influence of prescription and over-the-counter medications. The program shall be implemented in states or territories that are most affected by the opioid epidemic."
